1.2.name: wordpress/bubble-tooltip
1.2.description:
no development and no longer support

This plugin makes easy to use nice tooltips for your blog. You can change for two toolips.

Javascript for Bubble Tooltips is from Alessandro Fulciniti More informations about the script.

Javascript for Sweet Titles is from Dustin Diaz. More informations about the script.

Please visit the official website for further details and the latest information on this plugin.
